    a: 'Same categories as Infosys / TCS / HCLTech demonstrations — specific AI vendor spend; AI revenue contribution; integration-residual vendor overlap quantification; L&T group cross-entity cost allocation methodology; RCM and Section 195 TDS specifics; internal controls evidence. These require client cooperation.',
